== 1996 US DMC tournament ==
In 1996, as a first time entry, he won the DMC US DJ Championship.
After winning the 1996 US DMC Championships, Swamp found himself still driving a street sweeper for a living in Ohio.
He waited for Beck all day but never got to meet him.
A few weeks later Beck called Swamp
The two toured together for four years.
From 2016–2018 DJ Swamp toured as a member of the band Ministry.
After years of touring with Beck, DJ Swamp released his first album, "Never is Now", which was supported by the successful single "Worship the Robots."
